description:
Ultimate Retro Pack v1.00 by RXM420

Following the popularity of my Legendary Retro Pack, I present to you the Ultimate Retro Pack!

It contains even more:

Games and Emulators for 22+ Retro Game Systems!

All known NES ROMs
All known SNES ROMs
All known Nintendo 64 ROMs
All known Genesis / Mega Drive ROMs
All known Atari 2600 ROMs
All known Atari 5200 ROMs
All known Atari 7800 ROMs
All known GameBoy ROMs
All known GameBoy Color ROMs
All known GameBoy Advance ROMs
All known Sega GameGear ROMs
All known Sega Master System ROMs
All known Sega SG-1000 ROMs
6895 Arcade ROMs
139 Atari Jaguar ROMs
182 Neo Geo ROMs
45 Sega Dreamcast ROMs
14 PlayStation One (PSX) Games
2 Popular PS2 Games
5 Popular PSP Games
100 Nintendo DS ROMs
340 TurboGrafx-16 / PC Engine ROMs

I made sure I included all the BIOS files with the emulators that require them.

Every console emulated has it's own icon - create your own custom Retro desktop!

Comments are welcome!

PS. Some emulators may not work under your operating system, if so, just Google 'RetroArch' and run the ROMs that way.
